Package: r2x
Title: R2X - R to XML bridge
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Johannes Willkomm
Maintainer: Johannes Willkomm <johannes@johannes-willkomm.de>
License: GPL
Description: R2X is a simple R to XML bridge. Named lists are
 converted to XML elements by the r2x function. Values are rendered as
 attributes when they are plain values. XML documents are converted to
 named lists by the x2r function.
Depends: xml2, xslt
